# -*-cperl-*-

=head1 NAME

_HETERODYNE_HELLO_ - Initialization steps for heterodyne observations.

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This primitive performs initialization steps for heterodyne
observations. It sorts time-series data in increasing time order (see
_SORT_TIMESERIES_) and writes the results to $ORAC_DATA_OUT.

=head1 ARGUMENTS

=over 4

None.

=back

=head1 NOTES

=over 4

=item *

This primitive is suitable for all heterodyne instruments.

=back

=head1 OUTPUT DATA

=over 4

=item *

Time-sorted data with the _ts suffix appended.

=back

=head1 TASKS

See _SORT_TIMESERIES_.

=head1 REQUIRED PERL MODULES

None.

